descript.abstract: Polygon coverage of George Washington and Jefferson National Forests overstory vegetation. Coverage includes SAF forest type and age codes.
descript.purpose: To maintain National Forest overstory vegetation inventory for the George Washington and Jefferson National Forests. To map the overstory vegetation and faciltate the management of timber stand resources.
descript.supplinf: Digital data capture is by manual digitizing which carries inherent precision and accuracy limitations. The data may not meet National Map Accuracy Standards.

procstep.procdesc: Spatial data were field collected, tranferred to USGS 1:24,000 7.5 Minute Quads and manually digitized from base maps in ArcEdit. Attributes were manually entered from field observation data in Tables or ArcEdit.
